</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="224" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="31.[1461,2675,284,2409]" pageId="31" pageNumber="224">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1463,1597,1939,1972]" pageId="31" pageNumber="224">Breeding.</emphasis>
Nelson's Kangaroo Rat breed throughout the year, but most reproduction occurs in April-September and November.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
